snippet.title: Aquaman' Official Photo Grafic Trailer (2018) | Jason Momoa, Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Aquaman' Official Photo Grafic Trailer (2018) | Jason Momoa, Amber Heard  

Published on 5 Oct 2018

Watch the official extended trailer for DCEU adventure "Aquaman" starring Jason Momoa, Amber Heard, Willem Dafoe, Temuera Morrison, Dolph Lundgren, Yahya Abdul-Mateen II, Patrick Wilson, and Nicole Kidman. Directed by James Wan. Release date: December 21st, 2018 Plot Summary Aquaman finds himself caught between a surface world that ravages the sea and the underwater Atlanteans who are ready to revolt.
